QuestData.Title: Battle At The Iron Front
QuestData.Description: The war against the Iron horde rages on.$b$bNot far from here at The Iron Front, our warriors are engaged in mortal combat with the enemy. They fight tenaciously and with great fury, but the losses have been severe.$b$bGo to The Iron Front and show the enemy that we will not falter in this war.$b$bShow them that we fight as wolves!
QuestData.LogDescription: Aid the Alliance and Horde assault at The Iron Front in Tanaan Jungle.

Objectives.Objective: Aid In The Battle At The Iron Front
